data.description: FRESH TO MARKET !!!! A wonderful house near Lake Grassy with a amazing sunset view !!!  This is a large 3/2 home with a den that is currently being used as a 4th bedroom. It sits on a corner half an acre lot and a fenced in backyard which is perfect for children or pets. Has a lot of space & lots of potential for a nice pool outback or some landscape The front yard has been landscaped with rocks brought in from Montana and designer circular driveway. this home has had Quite a few upgrades per the owner: New shingle roof in 2019, New A/C and A/C ducts in 2019, New Well Bladder in 2019, new interior & exterior paint. Open Concept home with sunken living room and open kitchen and dining room Main floors of home are Travertine Marble , hallways a wood look floating floor & bedrooms & den are stamped concrete . Many windows and multiple sliding glass doors at the back of the house lets in a lot of natural light.has a very large back porch that was once covered but was damaged and removed from a hurricane owner works alot and has little time to tighten up the home so it does need some minor repairs here and there .there is a 10 x 18 shed in the back yard that stays with the property . just across the street is lake grassy and this home has unique position  that allows you a canal view to the lake with a amazing florida sunset . Don't miss out on this home !!!!
